{"tid":1563577,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[集思廣益]激勵現今各義士嘅歌","createTime":"2019-09-12T12:37:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-13T02:08:24.000Z","uid":144626,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"5bf53d5d2a4ebf66cf82f9ae532aab812bf30e6f","tid":1563577,"uid":144626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T12:37:15.000Z","msg":"除左<strong>榮耀歸於香港</strong>同埋<strong>1969年香港之歌</strong>呢幾首經典歌曲<br />\n其實香港粵語歌曲興盛時, 有唔少激勵人心嘅歌<br />\n唔係單單勵志，而係一鼓作氣，就好似行軍打仗咁樣<br />\n可以用黎前線播，用以激勵士氣亦有令人回憶起香港英國時期期光輝，而唔係左膠最愛We are the World呢類無關痛癢嘅歌<br />\n我有唔少例子：<br />\nBeyond: 不可一世、我是憤怒、長城<br />\n張國榮： 共創真善美、我走我路<br />\n許冠傑：做個自由人、同舟共濟、知恥近乎勇、腐朽化神奇、再會香港<br />\n關正傑：香江歲月<br />\n<br />\n我個人覺得<strong>做個自由人</strong>、<strong>我是憤怒</strong>同埋<strong>不可一世</strong>都好適合前線義士聽<br />\n用以震奮軍心最為有效<br />\n美國同法國首國歌，本身就有類似嘅功效<br />\n唔知大家嘅將軍令係邊首？<br />\n在此放埋上年影嘅香港日出<br />\n我已經一段時間冇揸機影日出日落<br />\n希望有日煲底可以同大家合照<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LmmTWeO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLmmTWeO.jpg&h=b43622ff&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"559594de3e94b027a87b1607e202f3d93672bfb8","tid":1563577,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T12:38:01.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=